node.text: The ocean means a lot to me and I want to do my 1% in taking care of it. If we can all do our part we can protect it for the future generations! I’m happy to be working with @shiseido as they are a part of the #WeAreOneOcean campaign. #ShiseidoSBAS #ShiseidoBlue @wsl @wslpure @shiseido

node.text:
The ocean has been my home since I was 3 years old. Surfing has made me into the person I am today... @beatsbydre 

3歳の頃から海がホームだった。サーフィンが僕をここまで成 ⻑させてくれた。そして何よりいつも応援してくれてるみんな
に感謝🙏 #beatsbydre

node.text: Such a special feeling to be here in Tokyo preparing for the Olympics. What better way to unite the world than through sport? In a time where we need it more than ever, I think we can spread a positive message and lift each other up. I can’t wait to represent my sport and country. Here we go 🥷

node.text: The ocean means a lot to me and I want to do my 1% in taking care of it. If we can all do our part we can protect it for the future generations! I’m happy to be working with @shiseido as they are a part of the #WeAreOneOcean campaign. #ShiseidoSBAS #ShiseidoBlue @wsl @wslpure @shiseido

node.text: What a fun event over the weekend, 3rd place. So much pressure and points on the line. Really happy with my performance and result. Back in the top 5 race and couldn’t have come at a better timing! Special Father’s Day this year! Onto the next one 🗡 @tsherms
